text: 35 Biggest Hits is a 2008 compilation album by country singer Toby Keith. It was released on 6 May, 2008. It went to number 1 in the United States and number 17 in Canada. ==Track listing== ===Disc 1=== ===Disc 2=== ==References== Category:2008 albums Category:Toby Keith albums
title: 35 Biggest Hits
